15. Create a PHP program to compute the sum of the digits of a number.

Code:
<?php
echo "Enter a number: ";
$number = trim(fgets(STDIN));

$sum = 0;

while ($number > 0) {
    $digit = $number % 10;     
    $sum += $digit;            
    $number = (int)($number / 10);  
}

echo "Sum of digits: $sum\n";
?>

Output:
Enter a number: 54
Sum of digits: 9
